snippet.title: Up To No Goob - Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out our new game Up To No Goob! A cozy bullethell where you play as Goob, a Goblin hungry for some breakfast, who steals ingredients from nearby towns. The nearby towns have some issues with this and retaliate with everything they've got: arrows, horses, Ultra Cannons... You know, the usual. So Goob up, it's time to make some breakfast!

Up To No Goob is coming to Steam on December 13th!

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2715620...

For more info, cute goobers and future updates visit our website: https://uptonogoob.carrd.co/
